":{"type":"keyword"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.theodi.org/with_tag.json?keyword=strategy","web_url":"http://theodi.org/tags/strategy","slug":"strategy"}},{"id":"https://contentapi.theodi.org/tags/keywords/innovation.json","web_url":null,"title":"innovation","details":{"type":"keyword"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.theodi.org/with_tag.json?keyword=innovation","web_url":"http://theodi.org/tags/innovation","slug":"innovation"}}],"details":{"business_proposition":false,"description":"","excerpt":"Data is changing the world. The Open Data Institute can help you to adapt and thrive. Find out what's possible...\r","language":"en","need_extended_font":false,"alternative_title":"","url":"","content":"<h3 id=\"dataischangingtheworldtheopendatainstitutecanhelpyoutoadaptandthrivefindoutwhatspossible\">Data is changing the world. The Open Data Institute can help you to adapt and thrive. Find out what's possible...</h3>\n<hr />\n<blockquote>\n  <p>All governments and businesses can use data to transform their work, create value and increase impact. The ODI and its global network are brilliantly positioned to help you in this age of data.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>â€” Sir Nigel Shadbolt and Sir Tim Berners-Lee, Founders</p>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"leadapositivechange\">Lead a positive change</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://bd7a65e2cb448908f934-86a50c88e47af9e1fb58ce0672b5a500.r32.cf3.rackcdn.com/uploads/assets/e5/04/58e50484f362be0890000009/CHANGEtn.jpg\" alt=\"Lead a positive change\" class=\"img pull-left\" id=\"58e504841f986a450900000a\">\nDo you want to unlock innovation in your organisation or lead positive change across your sector? Let us help you find the benefits of open data, publish or use it better and build trust amongst your community.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-info btn-lg \" href=\"http://theodi.org/lead-a-change\">Lead a positive change</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"findnewwaystoinnovate\">Find new ways to innovate</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://bd7a65e2cb448908f934-86a50c88e47af9e1fb58ce0672b5a500.r32.cf3.rackcdn.com/uploads/assets/e5/06/58e5066c1f986a47d1000007/Innovatetn.jpg\" alt=\"Innovate\" class=\"img pull-left\" id=\"58e5066cd0d462546a000012\">\nTo innovate or solve problems, you often need to look beyond your team or sector. Your next big idea might come from connecting with an organisation or government across the world with the knowledge to find your solution.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-info btn-lg \" href=\"http://theodi.org/find-new-ways-to-innovate\">Find new ways to innovate</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"buildasustainabledatastrategy\">Build a sustainable data strategy</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://bd7a65e2cb448908f934-86a50c88e47af9e1fb58ce0672b5a500.r32.cf3.rackcdn.com/uploads/assets/e5/07/58e50715f362be089000000c/Datastrategy.jpg\" alt=\"Data strategy\" class=\"img pull-left\" id=\"58e507151f986a450900000d\">\nDo you want to develop your leadership, future-proof your organisation or update your data policy? Through a bespoke approach from training to policy review, consultations to workshops, we can help you develop data strategies and policies that work for your team and in your context.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-info btn-lg \" href=\"http://theodi.org/build-a-sustainable-data-strategy\">Build a sustainable data strategy</a></p>\n<p></p>","media_enquiries_name":"","media_enquiries_email":"","media_enquiries_telephone":"","organizations":[],"author":{"name":"Hannah Foulds","slug":"hannah-foulds","state":"published","web_url":"http://theodi.org/team/hannah-foulds","tag_ids":["team","culture-programme","odi-team"]}},"related_external_links":[],"related":[{"id":"https://contentapi.theodi.org/contact.json","web_url":"http://theodi.org/contact","slug":"contact","title":"Contact Us","format":"article","updated_at":"2015-09-21T08:39:38+00:00","created_at":"2012-07-11T13:53:02+00:00","tag_ids":["page","contact","inquiries","address"]}],"organizations":[],"author":{"name":"Hannah Foulds","slug":"hannah-foulds","state":"published","web_url":"http://theodi.org/team/hannah-foulds","tag_ids":["team","culture-programme","odi-team"]}}